title: JRE Review of 1292 with Lex Fridman
description:
Lex is an MIT AI scientist and a really interesting person. This is his second time on Joe and he's really getting good on the podcast. Hopefully He'll become a regular and I like what he has to offer to the conversation. He's very well thought out and has some funny shit to say too. Loved it!
